data.description: Beautifully renovated Country Home on 1/2 an acre & less than 10 minutes from town. Home boasts 3 bedrooms + a bonus room, 2 bathrooms, and spacious living spaces. Enjoy the peace and tranquility country living has to offer. The exterior boasts a fully fenced yard, a new roof, dog run, large patio, a root cellar, and a spacious driveway ideally situated to fit all your vehicles with plenty of room to build a shop. Property is connected to a community water system and features a separate well for irrigation of grounds. Rare find, ZONED UR2 multi-family possibilities! Daycare, Senior Care and Cottage industry may be allowed subject to a Discretionary Use Permit, buyer to verify with county. Don't miss it & schedule a showing today!
